00:48:29.930 --> 00:48:32.500
And of course, thanks
to the HILT, the most

00:48:32.500 --> 00:48:33.950
magnificent conference.

00:48:33.950 --> 00:48:35.450
And thanks to all
of you for coming.

00:48:35.450 --> 00:48:37.950
